column5: Anyone fished it? Is there a camp there? Thinking about going up there with my girls this summer. From what I understand, theres walters to be had and a little venture by boat to get there. From the port loring area. Any info would be great Thanks in advance Vince

Try calling the local MNR office, vinnimon...the Parry Sound office probably covers that area....ask to talk to one of the biologists, and you may end up with some useful info.  They don't necessarily know all the lakes inside and out...but I've found it's usually worth a call.
Try calling Little River Lodge and Cabins You can boat to Chartier fron there. Ph.1-705-757-5723 mikdor
